# StudyAssistant – AI Powered Learning Assistant

StudyAssistant is an AI-powered web application designed to help students learn more efficiently by providing instant explanations, study guidance, and intelligent responses to academic questions.

The application uses Generative AI to simplify complex concepts and deliver personalized learning assistance directly through an interactive interface.

🚀 Live Demo:
https://huggingface.co/spaces/Shreyase/StudyAssistant

✨ Features
• AI-powered question answering for academic topics
• Personalized explanations based on selected learning style
• Fast and interactive interface using Gradio
• Built using modern Generative AI APIs
• Easy-to-use web interface for students

🧠 Use Cases
• Quick concept explanations
• Exam preparation support
• Homework help
• Self-paced learning

🛠 Tech Stack
• Python
• Generative AI API
• Gradio
• Hugging Face Spaces

🌍 Deployment
The application is deployed on Hugging Face Spaces for easy access and live interaction.

